{"page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Information Risk Management Plc\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Data Forensics Service\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    IRM recognise that due to technological advancements and a huge increase in communication and data sharing \u2013 personal and intellectual property can be attained by those with intent and access.  By employing an IRM data forensic consultant, your business would be able to confirm or negate any suspicion of wrongdoing.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Uncovers employee policy violations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reveals intellectual property theft, financial fraud and many other issues\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     An expert investigation conducted in IRM\u2019s forensic laboratory\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Conducts efficient and forensically sound data collection\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Track down deleted items, password protected files and hidden files\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Uses repeatable, secure processes to acquire data from multiple devices\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Conducted by a computer forensic expert\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Delivers a comprehensive logbook suitable as legal evidence\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Delivers an Executive Report including files structures, integrity and recoverability\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides detailed recommendations to allow you to move forward\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3100 per person per hour\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Education pricing available\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Termination costs apply\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Hour\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/93196/6217841820827648-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/93196/6217841820827648-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/93196/6217841820827648-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/93196/6217841820827648-terms-and-conditions.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Framework\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"external-link-default\">\n     <a href=\"http://ccs-agreements.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/contracts/rm1557vi\" rel=\"external\">\n      G-Cloud 6\n     </a>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Service ID\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"service-id\">\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      6217\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      8418\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      2082\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      7648\n     </span>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Contact\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-details\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">\n     <p class=\"contact-details-organisation\">\n      <span itemprop=\"name\">\n       Information Risk Management Plc\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\">\n       <span itemprop=\"name\">\n        Sean Arrowsmith\n       </span>\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemprop=\"telephone\">\n       01242 225 207\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemprop=\"email\">\n       <a data-event-category=\"Email a supplier\" data-event-label=\"Information Risk Management Plc\" href=\"mailto:GCloud@irmplc.com\">\n        GCloud@irmplc.com\n       </a>\n      </span>\n     </p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row service-attributes\">\n  <div class=\"column-one-whole\">\n   <h2 class=\"summary-item-heading\">\n    Support\n   </h2>\n   <table class=\"summary-item-body\">\n    <caption class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Support\n    </caption>\n    <thead class=\"summary-item-field-headings\">\n     <tr>\n      <th class=\"summary-item-field-heading-first\" scope=\"col\">\n       <span class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n        Name\n     